### Criar usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Adson4",
  "email": "adson4@email.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "CLIENTE"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "adson@email.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Me sem token (Deve dar 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me

### Me com token (deve dar 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Error genérico (para testar o fallback)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "invalido",
  "password": "1"
}

### Reception (deve 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/reception
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenGerencia}}

### Management (deve 403 para RECEPCAO)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/management
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenGerencia}}

### Maintenance (deve 403 para RECEPCAO)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/maintenance
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenGerencia}}

### Criar Quarto (deve 403 para RECEPCAO)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenGerencia}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": 101,
  "floor": 1,
  "dailyRate": 150.0
}

### listar quartos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### trocar status do quarto
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rooms/{{roomID}}/status?status=AVAILABLE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenGerencia}}

### Criando reserva
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 1,
  "guestId": 4,
  "checkInDate": "2026-03-05",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-03-06"
}

### Fazendo check-in
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings/{{roomID}}/check-in
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}